divs: Sighting DetailsMy family and i were staying in a country hotel it was a lovely sunny day with a slight breeze and we were about to leave when i took 2 pictures of the grounds only to find some strange objects on the first picture . It was not until we arrived home and i downloaded them onto my computer did i notice the strange objects. They may be nothing at all but if you could check them for me that would be great. Thanx for your time.
